high_descs: Move to the chan chair on the far left with the red credit card on top of it
Pick up the credit card on the chair
Carry the red credit card to the floor lamp in the corner of the room

high_descs: Turn around and walk past the black coffee table, then turn right and go past the first white arm chair, then stop and turn at the second white arm chair to your left.
Pick up the credit card on the seat of the white arm chair.
Turn around and walk between the couch and the coffee table to get across the room, to the lamp in the left corner.
Turn on the lamp in the left corner.
anns.task_desc: Turn on the lamp in the family room.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the chair to the left of the sofa, closest to the window, and with a red credit card on it
Pick up the red credit card from the chair
Turn to your right and carry the credit card past the sofa in front of the window to the lamp to the right of the sofa
anns.task_desc: Pick up a credit card, turn on a lamp
